                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/725.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-26T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1915—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Report results representations for modification mining decree March 1. Many
                    American citizens assert operation this decree would necessarily result in
                    confiscation their property and Department desires you take strong action on
                    this ground.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
